{'en': '## Space

We know that our guests value comfort and the opportunity to relax, so we focused on comfort and functionality, without giving up an interesting interior design. Elegant, spacious apartment is fully equipped with all necessary amenities.

## Access

The four-person studio apartment includes:
âœ“ large balcony

! We offer breakfast - PLN 35 per person, to be ordered at the reception, or immediately after booking

## Interaction

## Neighborhood

In the heart of GdaÅ„sk

Our Deo Residence & Spa apartments are located on Wyspa SpichrzÃ³w, on the MotÅ‚awa River itself. They are part of the Deo Plaza complex - it is a former granary, one of the three survivors of the war. Its current appearance retains the shape it was given before 1910 and after the fire of 1930. During the renovation, restoration measures were introduced to refer to the color of historic GdaÅ„sk (the color of the walls, shutter frames and entrances), showing respect for the historical values ​​of the building and the place.

Deo Residence is located on the MotÅ‚awa River itself, on the side of the island, on Chmielna - the main street of Wyspa SpichrzÃ³w. Perpendicular to the waterfront and Chmielna, Deo Residence borders on ul. StÄ…giewna, which crosses the Green Bridge and is an extension of the Long Market, and thus the Royal Route.

description:
{'en': '## Space

We know that our guests value comfort and the opportunity to relax, which is why we focused on comfort without giving up the decor.

Over 37 sq m included:
âœ“ elegant room with a kitchenette
âœ“ bedroom
âœ“ stylish bathroom
âœ“ storage room with washing machine and wardrobe

We offer breakfast - PLN 35 per person, to be ordered at the reception, or immediately after booking.

## Access

The highlight of the room is a very comfortable double bed.

The living room has been combined with an open kitchen, which gives the impression of additional space and makes spending time together more pleasant. A four-person table allows for comfort during meals that you will prepare in a fully equipped kitchen with a stove, oven and refrigerator.

A separate bedroom equipped with a large bed will ensure privacy.

A comfortable bathroom with a shower has all the necessary cosmetics, towels and a hair dryer.

## Interaction

âœ† Throughout the stay of guests, we are available by phone and in the office - ready to help in case of any problems.

## Neighborhood

In the heart of GdaÅ„sk

Our Deo Residence & Spa apartments are located on Wyspa SpichrzÃ³w, on the MotÅ‚awa River itself. They are part of the Deo Plaza complex - it is a former granary, one of the three survivors of the war. Its current appearance retains the shape it was given before 1910 and after the fire of 1930. During the renovation, restoration measures were introduced to refer to the color of historic GdaÅ„sk (the color of the walls, shutter frames and entrances), showing respect for the historical values ​​of the building and the place.

Deo Residence is located on the MotÅ‚awa River itself, on the side of the island, on Chmielna - the main street of Wyspa SpichrzÃ³w.
